            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce has thickened, stir the<strong> cooked spaghetti</strong> through the sauce with <strong>half</strong> the <strong>crispy meat-free bacon </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) and give everything a good mix up until the pasta is fully coated in the sauce – this is your <strong>plant-based gluten free spaghetti carbonara</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if the sauce is a little thick!</p><p>Wash your <strong>rocket</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
